commands:
-settings {setting} {true/false} = ADMIN ONLY! Allows the user to change bot settings
-versionnumber = Returns the current version
-credits = Shows credits and attributions
-latestupdate = Shows patch notes
-randomvideo = Shows a random youtube video
-randomgif = Shows a random gif
-randommusic = Shows a random song
-bulkdel {int} = ADMIN ONLY! Deletes a set number of messages
-rolecreate {name} {admin/normal} = ADMIN ONLY! Creates a new role
-roledelete {name} = ADMIN ONLY! Deletes an existing role
-ppsize = Dick size command (real)
-chatgpt {prompt (SPECIAL: accepts spaces) = Uses chatGPT
